@@$TJvCalculator
<TITLE TJvCalculator overview>
<GROUP JVCL.CommonDialogs>
  TJvCalculator is a non-visible component that serves as a wrapper around the calcuclator dialog.

  Execute the following tasks to use the component:
  * Specify the <LINK TJvCalculator.Title, title> for the dialog.
  * Specify an <LINK TJvCalculator.Value, initial value> for the calculator.
  * <LINK TJvCalculator.Execute, Activate> the dialog.
  * Retrieve the <LINK TJvCalculator.Value, result> from the calculation.
