@@TJvCalculator.Execute
Summary
  Displays the calculator.
Description
  Execute displays the calculator dialog. The calculator value is initialized to the value specified
  by the Value property. The caption of the dialog is set to the Title property.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCalculator.Title
Summary
  The caption of the calculator dialog.
Description
  Title is the caption of the calculator dialog.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCalculator.Value
Summary
  Initial value for or result of the calculator.
Description
  Value is the intial value for the calculator before the Execute method is called or the result
  when the Execute method returns.

  Set Value to an initial value for the calculator.

  Read Value to retrieve the result of the calculator.
